<HEADLINE>
<P>
CAMPAIGN FINANCING 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 From the most depressing election year in recent history emerges one 
undeniable fact: The privately financed campaign is killing democracy in 
America. 
</P>
<P>
 Whether the money comes from an individual, a corporation, a PAC or a 
candidate's own deep pocket, the result is the same -- "one dollar, one vote" 
replaces "one person, one vote." 
</P>
<P>
 There is one way out of this mess, and one way only: publicly financed 
campaigns. 
</P>
<P>
 MONTE MONTGOMERY 
</P>
<P>
 Crestline 
</P>
</TEXT>
