MAN DIES AFTER BEING HIT BY BUS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 A man who appeared to be a transient rolled off a bus bench Tuesday and was 
hit and killed by an MTA bus, authorities said. 
</P>
<P>
