<P>
 Microsoft, Visa to Develop Secure Electronic Payment System: The software 
giant and the credit card purveyor said they will work together to develop a 
secure method for transmitting credit-card information between buyers and 
merchants.The effort could eventually make it much easier for customers and 
merchants to conduct business over the Internet computer network or other 
on-line computer services. The technology will be based on Microsoft's popular 
