<DATE>
<P>
November 9, 1994, Wednesday, Home Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Part A; Page 4; Column 1; Foreign Desk 
</P>
</SECTION>
<LENGTH>
<P>
411 words 
</P>
