<HEADLINE>
<P>
CALIFORNIA ELECTIONS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Contributing to The Times' election coverage were staff writers Eric Bailey, 
Glenn F. Bunting, Miguel Bustillo, Frank Clifford, Ricard Colvin, Rich Connell, 
