By JEFF BEAN 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Saddleback College's Outdoor Marketplace will have its grand opening at 8 a.m. 
Saturday. 
</P>
<P>
 The swap meet will include vendors selling arts and crafts, antiques, 
clothing, sporting goods and professional services. 
</P>
<P>
 The marketplace will be held every weekend in parking lot 10 at the campus 
from 8 a.m. to 4 p.m. The school is at 28000 Marguerite Parkway. 
</P>
<P>
