ORANGE COUNTY BRIEFLY 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Tri-Lite Inc.: The firm said Tuesday that its Prolite unit has formed a 
partnership with HLFC Inc. to provide $20 million in financing to upgrade 
lighting fixtures at McDonald's, Wendy's and Burger King restaurants. 
</P>
<P>
 The finance company in Naples, Fla., will provide funds to franchisees who 
wish to install energy-saving lighting equipment. 
</P>
<P>
 The Irvine lighting fixture manufacturer said it has received orders to 
inspect 1,240 Burger King franchises. 
</P>
